cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is about person re-identification, which is a computer vision task related to image and video analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel adversarial learning method, which is a popular technique in machine learning, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category. Additionally, the paper involves deep learning models and optimization algorithms, which are related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also uses large-scale datasets, which is related to cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper deals with security and privacy issues related to surveillance cameras, which is related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
